{
  "stem": "1061.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, I shouldn't be saying that, but-- because human beings know how to-- how to come across when there's need, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When people see a little kid, and it's full of lice and starved to death, and she's all left alone, somebody will hug her, you see?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because the world is like this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "On one end, you have this horror of the German beast with the dogs or the Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "On the other hand, you have this little old lady who will hug a little skinny kid filled with, covered with lice.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So anyhow, my sisters were my protectors, and they were my guardians, and they were-- they were my surrogate parents.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And of course, the fact that every now and then we could see Father-- you know, wave to him or whatever-- was very helpful.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We lived in barracks, of course, in that camp, [INAUDIBLE] But in the last camp where the breakout took place, that-- I don't even remember if there was a real camp or if they would just dumped us there.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it was transitional in a way of it probably took a day or two or three at the most.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the trains that were on that siding-- because, as you know, a factory like this must have a siding near it for transporting the-- the the goods to the factory and back-- that siding was used for the trains onto which this last camp was emptied onto those trains.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody that was not killed in the-- in the-- in the breakout the night before.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody who survived the horror of typhus, of starvation, of beating, of working to death in the factories.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
